📊 InvestAI Chat Bot
📌 About

InvestAI Chat Bot is an intelligent assistant designed to help users explore and understand the stock market in a simple and interactive way. 
It provides real-time financial data, market insights, and sentiment analysis for specific stock tickers.
The bot is built to support both beginners and experienced investors by delivering key stock metrics and relevant news in an easy-to-digest format.

Features:

📈 Real-Time Stock Data
Open, High, Low, Close prices
Trading volume
📰 Financial News
Latest news for selected stock tickers
💬 Sentiment Analysis
Analyze market sentiment based on news data
⚡ Fast & Interactive Chat Interface

Future Improvements:(Important!!)
Integration of RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) for smarter responses
Enhanced prediction and analytics features
Portfolio tracking capabilities
Personalized investment insights

Tech Stack:
Python
APIs for real-time stock data by "MASSIVE"
Chatbot framework by Gradio
Ai-Frontier model by OpenAI -brend new GPT 5.4-the fastest one!


